A total of 13 people were hospitalized with suspected Siberian anthrax in Kara-Kuldja district of Osh region, the chief doctor of the regional General Practice Center Chynara Karmyshakova told Turmush... [more]

[This story is by subscription and I have found nothing else on Google. Osh is one of the oldest cities in the world. - Corr.SB]

